biography: Here we have Joakim, a golfer whose dedication to the sport is as noteworthy as his commitment to fair play. Although details regarding his home club remain private, Joakim's presence is always felt on the course.
Joakim is known for his level-headedness under pressure, a trait admired by his peers. He has participated in the Hector Trophée once.

While he has yet to secure a victory at the Hector Trophée or claim the Victor Trophy, his participation in the tournament speaks volumes about his passion for the game. Although Joakim will not be competing in the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025, the possibility of a late entry remains.
